OL,3,CQuestions raised over using former
OL,4,Cairbase for asylum seekers
OL,6,FPlans to use a former RAF base in
OL,7,FLincoln for asylum seeker housing are
OL,8,Fback in the headlines.
OL,10,FIn March 2023, it was announced RAF
OL,11,FScampton was to house 2,000 migrants
OL,12,Fas part of proposals by the previous
OL,13,FConservative government to reduce the
OL,14,Freliance on hotels.
