OL,3,CQuestions raised over using former
OL,4,Cairbase for asylum seekers
OL,6,FThe scheme was met with widespread
OL,7,Fanger after a huge local campaign -
OL,8,Falongside a business plan to transform
OL,9,Fthe site into a business hub including
OL,10,Fa heritage centre - a nod to its
OL,11,Fformer use as the base for the
OL,12,FDambusters in World War Two.
OL,14,FPlans were scrapped in September as
OL,15,Fpart of an election pledge by the new
OL,16,FLabour administration.
