OL,3,CQuestions raised over using former
OL,4,Cairbase for asylum seekers
OL,6,FHowever, on Monday 8 September Defence
OL,7,FMinister Luke Pollard said they had to
OL,8,F"look at every single site again" as
OL,9,Fpart of Labour's plan to close all
OL,10,Fasylum hotels.
OL,12,FWhen asked specifically about using
OL,13,FRAF Scampton, Mr Pollard said: "Well,
OL,14,Fall military sites and the ones that
OL,15,Fhave closed recently are part of our
OL,16,Fongoing work here because we want to
OL,17,Fsee every single asylum hotel closed.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
