OL,3,CQuestions raised over using former
OL,4,Cairbase for asylum seekers
OL,6,F"It's right that we look at every
OL,7,Fsingle site again, checking whether it
OL,8,Fcan be suitable for the temporary but
OL,9,Fadequate accommodation that we seek to
OL,10,Fbuild."
OL,12,FThose behind the local campaign to
OL,13,Fstop the base being used for asylum
OL,14,Fseekers said it's just over a year
OL,15,Fsince the Government decided to
OL,16,Fabandon the idea. They said it was a
OL,17,Fheadache, but one they're prepared for.
