OL,3,CQuestions raised over using former
OL,4,Cairbase for asylum seekers
OL,6,FSarah Carter, from Save Our Scampton,
OL,7,Fsaid: "I don't think (the Government)
OL,8,Fappreciate or understand what it does
OL,9,Fto the community and how it affects us
OL,10,Fhaving this over our head and last.
OL,12,F"You said you were going to put it on
OL,13,Fthe open market - it's still not on
OL,14,Fthe open market yet.
OL,16,F"What are you playing at? You are
OL,17,Frisking this #300m deal that we have
OL,18,Fgot. You are risking the sanity of the
OL,19,Fresidents who live here, and the wider
OL,20,Fcommunity"
