OL,3,CQuestions raised over using former
OL,4,Cairbase for asylum seekers
OL,6,FScampton Holdings is trying to develop
OL,7,Fthe site. They're keen to push ahead
OL,8,Fwith regeneration plans to create a
OL,9,Fhub for heritage, aviation, defence
OL,10,Fand space.
OL,12,FPeter Hewitt, from Scampton Holdings,
OL,13,Fsaid: "This is #2.1 billion of benefit
OL,14,Fto the local economy and the economy
OL,15,Fas a whole. I think the message is
OL,16,Fever so simple - the Home Office who
OL,17,Fnow own the site must make their mind
OL,18,Fup, get on with it and stop being
OL,19,Findecisive."
